cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.MA, cs.SY 

The paper deals with the analysis of human body blockage in millimeter-wave cellular communications, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The use of millimeter-wave frequencies is also a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM) and mobile computing (cs.MA). Additionally, the proposed model for characterizing blocking can be applied to system optimization and control (cs.SY).
